    "The IoT agriculture market is growing due to the increasing popularity of technology and the telecommunications industry.",
    "Farmers can now use smartphones to track and monitor their agricultural operations, accessing precise data.",
    "These factors are expected to drive the demand for smart agriculture in the future.",
    "According to a report by Precedence Research, the IoT market in agriculture has shown significant growth over time.",
    "In 2021, it was valued at $12.15 billion and experienced considerable growth, reaching $13.70 billion in 2022."
